reviewText: This Tournament Of Death Is One The Best Ones That Czw Has Had. Features Some Pretty Good Wrestlers. Theres Quite A Few Awesome Matches In This Dvd. The Three Best Matches Are Sexxxy eddy vs Arsonist. During that match he cuts an artery in his wrist and at the end squirts blood from his arm into his own mouth. It's pretty messed up. Then Necro Butcher .vs. green phantom, features some sick lightube shots and then last but not least the finals. Necro Butcher takes on Wifebeater. Some of the most violent lightube shots I've seen and then the ending. Wifebeater then throws Necro off a moving truck through Tables And Flaming pane of glass. Yes I said flaming! It was insane. If you wanna see dome crazy hardcore wrestling. Get This! :)
